# Design System Adherence

- Treat Figma frame `26:15603` as the current source of truth for the top-level index page styles.
- Keep `features/design-system/tokens.ts` limited to the colors and font styles shown in that frame.
- Use `/style-guide` only as an unlinked internal reference for the top-level `app/page.tsx`.
- Do not apply this style guide to `app/ctv`, `app/campaign-planner`, `features/ctv`, or `features/campaign-planner`.
- Do not add assets, spacing, radius, shadows, or component examples until the user provides them.
